{"TopicId":157949,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"A Challenge for DLC code?","CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T00:32:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T00:32:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile I will buy the DLC, I am concerned about those that cannot afford it. Would SQUAD be making\u00A0a challenge/contest to give out the upcoming DLC? If not, would us community be willing to do so --\u00A0and if so, how do you think we should do it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kubas_inko","CreatedById":169457,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T06:08:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDOC!!? What, where, when, why?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rkarmark","CreatedById":158904,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T06:33:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA dlc is a paid adon to a game \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/169457-kubas_inko/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022169457\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/169457-kubas_inko/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kubas_inko\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/157802-ksp-making-history/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-20T06:33:32Z\u0022 title=\u002203/20/2017 06:33  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 20, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by rkarmark\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kubas_inko","CreatedById":169457,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-20T06:59:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat sucks. I \u00A0bought\u00A0the game in October 2013 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T00:38:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI bought mine at Dec 2013 steam sales. The DLC, even full price, is better than those from EA or OVK.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long as they don\u0027t do loot box and keys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T01:00:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222992232\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157949\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490056691\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165777\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jestersage\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, Jestersage said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI bought mine at Dec 2013 steam sales. The DLC, even full price, is better than those from EA or OVK.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long as they don\u0027t do loot box and keys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBTW even though I bought KSP right before the DLC period ended, I\u0027ve gotten so much enjoyment out of this game that I\u0027d gladly throw another $100 at SQUAD (about 4x what I paid for KSP!) just\u00A0to show my appreciation (not even for a DLC!).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T03:43:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince this thread is not itself a challenge, it has been moved to Suggestions.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-21T03:52:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis discussion will be relevant when we know the price. It might be so low that it\u0027s not even worth discussing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}